        <li>---. 2022. "Blackpill Science: Involuntary Celibacy, Rational Technique, and Economic Existence under Neoliberalism." <em>Canadian Journal of Communications 47</em> (4): 676-701. <a href="https://doi.org/10.3138/cjc.2022-07-25" class="accent-text hover:underline">https://doi.org/10.3138/cjc.2022-07-25</a>.</li>
        <li>Elmer, Greg and Anthony G. Burton. 2022. "Rebel personalities: Canada's far-right media." <em>First Monday</em> 27 (9). <a href="https://doi.org/10.5210/fm.v27i5.12546" class="accent-text hover:underline">https://doi.org/10.5210/fm.v27i5.12546</a>.</li>
      </ul>

