        <li>Jucan, Ioana B., Roopa Vasudevan, Anthony Glyn Burton, Tong Wu, and Yuguang (YG) Zhang. 2021. "Performing Left and Right." <em>Theatre Journal 73</em> (3): E-9. <a href="https://doi.org/10.1353/tj.2021.0064" class="accent-text hover:underline">https://doi.org/10.1353/tj.2021.0064</a>.</li>
