        <li>Burton, Anthony Glyn. 2019. "Being in/of the Network: The Chad Meme as Digital Subject". <em>To Be Decided: Journal of Interdisciplinary Theory</em>. 4 (2): 8.</li>
        <li>---. 2016. "The Production of Society: Social Cohesion, Newspapers, and Social Media". <em>ImagiNATIONS</em> 4 (1): 57--70.</li>
      </ul>

